                                    <li>Version 3.x (now discontinued) supports also old .NET Framework versions (from 3.5 till 4.6).</li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                            <div class="mt-4">
                                <a href="/download/eqn_asp_setup.exe" class="button primary">Download Free Trial</a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
