                                    <li>Supported Delphi versions: 6.0 and higher.</li>
                                    <li>Supported databases: Paradox, MS Access, MS SQL Server, Oracle, MySQL, PostgreSQL as well as any other database which can be used with Delphi or C++ Builder.</li>
